{"type": "article", "id": 5239, "title": "智能电动单车 508 E-Bike", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-15T07:59:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233528RptYwUNvzMr7yC8E.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t工业设计师杨明洁应东风标致邀请，为其设计了一款智能电动单车 508 E-Bike，设计师尝试捕捉雄狮轮廓的力量感，进而运用到单车的轮廓设计上。508 E-Bike 车身重量为 25.7 公斤，27 寸轮毂，后轮车架部分安装了 250 瓦中心曲柄结构电力发动装置，内置 36 伏锂电池。它的前轮内置有发电装置，可以将骑行时的动能转化为电能，支持车灯照明、导航设备、扬声器、手机充电等功能，最高时速可达 23.5 公里/小时，续航能力 87 公里 。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233526UqmpvnSrJMN5uKkC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335274CYy3W9LcuBD7PZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233527vuBKnYhsm8UNGJTq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233528JY2ISTuVGM7WFD9Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}